<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ZEIZONG VIALTE JESUH SINAH KA PEK LAI CH365</title>
<key>D</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Zeizong hlawt tak in ka Khamhtu Nangmah kha kan zulh lai ta; Maw ka
 Bawipa, nangmah lei ah, Na lam kha kan hmuhsak tuah.

[C1]
   Zeizong te ka pek, Zeizong te ka pek, Zeizong te Bawipa kut chungah,
   Keimah nih ka pek (Zeizongte ka pek)

[V2]
 Maw ka Khamhtu Bawi, keimah nih Nangmah sinah naih ka duh; Ngaihchin
 in kan halnak bia kha, Ngai law, ka khamh tuah, Bawipa.

[C2]
   Zeizong te ka pek, Zeizong te ka pek, Zeizong te Bawipa kut chungah,
   Keimah nih ka pek (Zeizongte ka pek)

[V3]
 Maw a ka Khamhtu, keimah nih Vawlei lawmhnak ka chiahtak; Thiang
 Thlarau in, maw ka Bawipa, Rung um tuah ka lung chungah.

[C3]
   Zeizong te ka pek, Zeizong te ka pek, Zeizong te Bawipa kut chungah,
   Keimah nih ka pek (Zeizongte ka pek)

[V4]
 Maw kan Khamhtu Bawi, keimah nih, Khamhnak hla kha ka sak lai, Vancung
 ram tha ka phak hlan tiang, Nangmah thawngin kaa lawm lai.

[C4]
   Zeizong te ka pek, Zeizong te ka pek, Zeizong te Bawipa kut chungah,
   Keimah nih ka pek (Zeizongte ka pek)</lyrics>
<hymn_number>365</hymn_number>
</song>